rules.SQL: SELECT CONCAT('http://www.owl-ontologies.com/Ontology1207768242.owl#ns/', A."c0") AS VAR10000,  'http://www.owl-ontologies.com/Ontology1207768242.owl#StockExchangeMember' AS VAR10002 FROM "src_StockExchangeList" as A, "src_Company" as B, "src_isExecutedBy" as C, "src_StockTrader" as D, "src_StockExchangeMember" as E WHERE  A."c0" = B."c0" AND B."c0" = C."c0" AND C."c0" = D."c0" AND D."c0" = E."c0" ;

SELECT CONCAT('http://www.owl-ontologies.com/Ontology1207768242.owl#ns/', "c0") AS VAR10500, CONCAT('http://www.owl-ontologies.com/Ontology1207768242.owl#ns/', "c1") AS VAR10502  FROM "src_belongsToCompany" ;
